*   ## **_SAMI ZAYN DEF. LUDWIG KAISER_**
    

Simple match that saw Sami Zayn fight from under the brutish Ludwig Kaiser style.

Post match, GUNTHER runs out and he seems frustrated. He tells Sami that it's clear he really wants the World Championship match at Bad Blood. But then GUNTHER laughs, he tells Sami no and then he leaves.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9d97790f-9b2d-40f0-98b7-42e6dcbf300d/Screenshot_20240923_173712.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7aa656a0-f599-43b9-a5ad-50b29f7c0b2f/20240923_174023.jpg?format=original)

The New Day is backstage and Kofi wants Xavier to go back to the old stuff with him. Xavier says that was cool when they were on top but they haven't been champs in 3 years.

Kofi says he understands. Then he says Xavier should be in charge. They're cool with each other.

American Made walks up and laughs at their efforts. So Xavier says his first play is to get a match against Them.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/59f74af2-ee75-4c8c-91ef-9169c4359a36/20240923_175725.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_DRAGON LEE DEF. CARLITO_**
    

Pretty quick match. Dom and JD fight off the LWO on the outside until Rey comes out and surprises them.

This all distracts Carlito and allows for Dragon Lee to take the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/14899f7a-70e4-4b68-8fde-8ed8b1f54477/20240923_175758.jpg?format=original)

The Miz wants to know why Karrion Kross has been bothering him. Karrion says he just wants the Miz to be himself again.

