Drew McIntyre is out to respond to CM Punk but this crowd is doing those really outdated WHAT chants the entire time.

Drew says Punk's family isn't the only one begging him not to get in the Cell. Drew's wife has begged Drew to get away from Punk. She can see what this is going to him.

Drew is gonna make Punk bleed.. a lot.

