*   ## **_AMERICAN MADE DEF. THE NEW DAY_**
    

CLEAN WIN over the New Day for American Made. This can't be good for the boys 😬

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f09bcec2-9176-4c67-b18a-173a6514e037/FB_IMG_1727147251916.jpg?format=original)

Xavier Woods and Kofi are backstage and things seem ok until the LWO walks up to clarify they didn't mean to mess things up last week.

Woods doesn't care. Says Rey should be giving advice to his son, not them. Rey says he doesn't have time for this because he has to focus on Finn Balor next week.

Woods starts crashing out. Rey and Finn are former world champs so he doesn't matter then?

Rey says you know what? Forget Finn Balor, REY VS WOODS NEXT WEEK

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5d3d32cb-c2aa-4f0b-b851-5da6bfb664d0/20240923_200103.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: JEY USO DEF BRON BREAKKER(c)_**
    

Whay a freaking match!! Jey Uso wins his first ever singles championship over Bron Breakker in a top notch match. Go out of your way to see it.